&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here I&#39;ll &lt;del&gt;shit&lt;/del&gt;post about tech, and maybe even other stuff I&#39;m interested in.&lt;/p&gt;
